Bingham Canyon Mine - Wikipedia






















 






Bingham Canyon Mine

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For the former city at this location, see Bingham Canyon, Utah.

Bingham Canyon Mine


Mine in 2003



Location









Bingham Canyon Mine








Location
Salt Lake County


