United States


Coordinates
40°31′23″N 112°09′04″W﻿ / ﻿40.523°N 112.151°W﻿ / 40.523; -112.151Coordinates: 40°31′23″N 112°09′04″W﻿ / ﻿40.523°N 112.151°W﻿ / 40.523; -112.151


Production


Products
Copper


