	certifies pursuant to Section 906 of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002 that:


	 







	a.




	the quarterly report on Form 10-Q of Bingham Canyon Corporation for
	the quarter ended March 31, 2017 fully complies with the requirements of Section 13(a) or 15(d) of the Securities Exchange
	Act of 1934; and





	 







	b.




	the information contained in the Form 10-Q fairly presents, in all material
	respects, the financial condition and results of operations of Bingham Canyon Corporation.





	 


	 





	 


	 


